Official Page of Montauk Brewing Company + Montauk Hard Seltzer - Must be 21+ to follow.
“Come As You Are”

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of nature and ocean.

node.text: Fall Vibes today in Montauk. Stock up on Montauk Pumpkin Ale, pack the cooler, go fish, go surf, go outside - you’ll be thankful you did. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk Brewing Company. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Green Toucan IPA is a beer that we've brewed a couple of times. Each time our fans go wild and ask for more of the bird. Well, if you are one of those people, you're in luck because a fresh batch of Green Toucan will be coming off the line at noon this Thursday.  Brewed with Citra, Idaho 7 and Strata hops and coming in at 6.5% ABV, this beer is packed with tropical and citrus notes with just the right amount of haze. This beer will fly, see you Thursday! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: Fall’s Fave is back! Ask for Montauk Pumpkin Ale at your favorite place to stock up on beer throughout Long Island, Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, The Bronx, Staten Island, Westchester, Rockland and Putnam counties! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: At about 11:59AM today, there was a line of smiling humans who were ready to enjoy some fresh craft beer. At 12:01PM those people were enjoying their beer. Today was a good day @montaukbrewco and those good vibes are certainly still going strong! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: Montauk Blueberry Ale is now on tap exclusively @montaukbrewco - Clocking in at 4.7%, and brewed with blueberries grown right up the road from the brewery, this beer is super refreshing and endlessly delicious! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: Our guess is that you might have a furry  copilot that could use a Montauk Summer Ale dog toy. You get the ice cold @montaukbrewco and the dog gets the toy, everybody wins. Link in bio! #montauk #comeasyouare #nationaldogday

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. on August 25, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Today was Wednesday, but it felt like a Friday because we have the best fans who seem to love fresh beer and good vibes, and that’s kinda our thing. The beers were flowing, we saw the occasional, yet well timed hi-five. Today was a good day. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of text that says '"COME AS YOU ARE: MONTAUK SIX OZCANS EASY RISER BELGIAN WHITE gia Style Wheat Ale 5.0% ALC/VOL'.

node.text: Over the next few weeks we will be announcing some exciting news on upcoming beer releases. Here’s one that we’ve been working on for quite some time now. Easy Riser is our take on a Belgian-Style Wheat Ale. Mellow and easy going, like a gently rising wave as it approaches the shore, this brew is the perfect expression of The Montauk Vibe - embodying the pure, relaxed enjoyment of the No-Frills Good Life. Brewed with coriander and orange peel, Easy Riser is incredibly smooth and, as the name suggests, incredibly easy to love. Ask for Easy Riser on tap at your favorite bar and be on the lookout for six packs in the coming weeks! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Montauk Brewing Co. in Montauk, New York. May be an image of cloud, nature and ocean.

node.text: Fun things are on the horizon - stay tuned. There’s things like new Ocean Series limited releases, a local Blueberry Ale, Montauk Pumpkin Ale returns and so much more. Have a nice little Tuesday! #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: Head over to our online store for old favorites and new hits. Looks like this season’s top seller is the crew neck sweatshirt. Super soft, extra cozy and perfect for those summer nights! Link in bio. #montauk #comeasyouare

node.text: Stock up on all the necessities including ice cold @montaukbrewco ahead of the storm! The taproom will be closed tomorrow out of an abundance of caution for our team and fans. Believe us, the dog isn’t pumped about this storm either. #montauk #comeasyouare
